  "instructions": [
    "Combine gochujang, soy sauce, chili flakes, brown sugar, and garlic in a blender or food processor and blend until smooth.",
    "Heat sesame oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add blended sauce to the saucepan and cook for 2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Add shrimp to the saucepan and cook until pink and cooked through, about 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add rice cakes to the saucepan and cook for an additional 2-3 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Garnish with green onions and sesame seeds, if desired.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
